; Simple Beancount File
; Basic transactions for testing parser

2014-01-01 open Assets:US:BofA:Checking
2014-01-01 open Assets:US:BofA:Savings
2014-01-01 open Income:US:Acme:Salary
2014-01-01 open Expenses:Food:Groceries
2014-01-01 open Expenses:Taxes

; Opening balance
2014-01-01 * "Initial deposit"
  Assets:US:BofA:Checking  1000.00 USD
  Income:US:Acme:Salary  -1000.00 USD

; Weekly groceries
2014-01-15 * "Whole Foods" "Weekly groceries"
  Assets:US:BofA:Checking  -75.50 USD
  Expenses:Food:Groceries  75.50 USD

; Savings transfer
2014-01-20 * "Transfer to savings"
  Assets:US:BofA:Checking  -200.00 USD
  Assets:US:BofA:Savings  200.00 USD

; Salary deposit
2014-02-01 * "Acme Corp" "Bi-monthly salary"
  Assets:US:BofA:Checking  3000.00 USD
  Income:US:Acme:Salary  -3000.00 USD

; Taxes
2014-02-01 * "Federal taxes"
  Assets:US:BofA:Checking  -500.00 USD
  Expenses:Taxes  500.00 USD